EngLawArticles.EngArticleContent:
A government agency, institution, organization, or individual that has practiced meteorological service and satisfies one of the following requirements may submit an application or through a recommendation to the CWB with an application form (or a recommendation letter) and associated documents in accordance with the second paragraph of Article 2:
1. promoting meteorological service with top performance;
2. advancing research and development in meteorological related technology with top performance;
3. engaged in meteorological-related disaster prevention education with top performance.
For a government agency, institution, organization, or individual satisfying the preceding requirements, the CWB may suggest the MOTC to grant an award and/or commendation in accordance with the first paragraph of Article 2.
The format of application form and the recommendation letter aforementioned in the first paragraph shall be established by the CWB.
